features: √ CONSOLE TABLE: This entry table combines wood grain finishes and black metal frames, creating an elegant and rustic atmosphere. The narrow console table takes up small space to provide multiple options for storage, display, and more. Perfect for entryways, hallways, foyers, corridors, space behind sofa couches, and any other narrow spaces in your home. The sofa table blends industrial, modern and traditional retro farmhouse to complement any decor and add appeal to your home.

√ ROBUST BUILD: Our console table is crafted from high-grade MDF engineered wood and heavy-duty metal, ensuring it's strong and durable. The solid tabletop provides excellent stability and durability, and the entry table to bear up to 110 lbs, which is more than enough for your needs. The sides of the sofa table feature X-shaped metal tubes, making it stable and shake-free. With high-quality materials and excellent craftsmanship, it can withstand extended use without fear of wear and tear.

√ NARROW CONSOLE TABLE: 33.5”L x 11.8”W x 31.8”H, providing an ideal storage solution that can fit in any narrow space. The 2 open shelves offer ample space for books, plants, lamps, decorations, and more. 4 Adjustable footpads are designed for leveling or uneven, protecting your tile and wood floors from scratches. The sofa table is versatile enough to serve as a foyer or entry table to welcome keys, hats, and other small items or as a behind couch table, Cleaning and maintaining it is a breeze.

√ EXTRA STORAGE SPACE: This rustic sofa table with open shelf is a versatile foyer table for your entryway. The bottom tier of the 2-tier sofa table provides an ideal spot for additional storage, whether it be for shoes, baskets, or anything else. By fully utilizing the available space, you'll have all your daily essentials easily within reach, ensuring a neat and tidy home or office. The long and skinny shape allows the industrial entryway table hidden behind the couch or under the window.

√ EASY to ASSEMBLY: This brown sofa table has been checked and is well-packed before shipping. You don't need to worry about assembly, the narrow entryway table comes with detailed installation instructions, parts and accessories are labeled with numbers, and precise holes make installation accurate and fast. 1-2 people can assemble in about 30 minutes. If you have any questions before or after your purchase, you can always email us, and we always reply within 24 hours.
